OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The longest-surviving heart transplant 
OL,6, patient has been recognised by Guinness
OL,7, World Records.                         
OL,9,FBert Janssen, 57, from the Netherlands,
OL,10,Fhas survived almost 40 years with the  
OL,11,Fdonor heart he received at Harefield   
OL,12,FHospital in Uxbridge, north-west       
OL,13,FLondon, in the 1980s.                  
OL,15,FHe was treated for cardiomyopathy,     
OL,16,Fwhich affects the heart's ability to   
OL,17,Fpump blood around the body.            
OL,19,FHe said he was "still grateful for the 
OL,20,Fincredible gift" his donor gave him.   
